<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545, #b02a37); color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #e9ecef; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #dc3545; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 15px; }
        .footer { padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.85em; color: #888; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h2>⚠️ Toxic Content Alert</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>The AI filter detected potentially toxic content on the platform.</p>

        <div style="background: #fff; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p><strong>User:</strong> {{ user.fullName }} ({{ user.email }})</p>
            <p><strong>Context:</strong> {{ context }}</p>
            <p><strong>Detection Source:</strong> <span style="background: #e2e8f0; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em;">{{ source }}</span></p>
            <p><strong>Content:</strong></p>
            <blockquote style="font-style: italic; color: #555;">
                "{{ content }}"
            </blockquote>
        </div>

        <p>Please review this user's activity appropriately.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>EduLink — Admin Alert System</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
